instruction: List the main characters and their characteristics in the given story
input: The story is about a young girl who discovers a magical world
output:
The main characters in the story are: 

•The girl – brave, adventurous, and curious 
•The magical people – wise, mysterious, and powerful 
•The magical creatures – friendly, loyal, and protective 
•The magical objects – imbued with mysterious powers 
•The evil force – powerful, determined, and ruthless
